      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing a steady daily driver. The exterior shows visible signs of its history, including several noticeable scratches along the doors and a few small dings on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate wear and some fading from sun exposure. Mechanically, it remains sound and has been regularly serviced, though it lacks the pristine finish of a newer model. It\u2019s a solid, functional car that is ready for the road, provided you don't mind a bit of character in its appearance.",
