      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been pampered, garage-kept, and is spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one. Come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
