    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, powered by the S54B32 power plant featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The vehicle has undergone a comprehensive mechanical vetting, including a documented rear subframe reinforcement and a full cooling system refresh. Every component, from the MacPherson strut front suspension to the multi-link rear, operates with factory-new tolerances. Featuring original paint depth and a pristine undercarriage, this is an investment-grade example for the serious collector.",
